Date: Tue, 8 Jun 1999 15:25:45 -0300
From: Fernando Dias de Avila Pires <favila@matrix.com.br>

Just a reminder on plague control. Advice to control rodents should be
accompanied by a recommendation also to control fleas. Killing rodents
liberate infected fleas. So, a campaign against rodents must be followed by
the use of insecticides.
--
